{"tid":109783,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"騰雞女學神 撞壆翻車","createTime":"2017-02-06T08:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T08:12:18.000Z","uid":41045,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6089c9e77aa0926273196e14a6e3a854c1013ad","tid":109783,"uid":41045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:01:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E9%A8%B0%E9%9B%9E%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%B8%E7%A5%9E-%E6%92%9E%E5%A3%86%E7%BF%BB%E8%BB%8A-221017115.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E9%259B%259E%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%25A5%259E-%25E6%2592%259E%25E5%25A3%2586%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E8%25BB%258A-221017115.html&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfp54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=219738a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E9%A8%B0%E9%9B%9E%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%B8%E7%A5%9E-%E6%92%9E%E5%A3%86%E7%BF%BB%E8%BB%8A-221017115.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【東方日報專訊】【本報訊】騰雞女學神撞翻車，兩師徒一度被困！昨午四時許，一輛屬於駕駛學校的私家車，由姓陳（廿四歲）女學員駕駛，由教車師傅在旁指導駕駛技術，當該車沿青山公路葵涌段往荃灣行駛時，途至港鐵大窩口站對開，突然失控撞向分隔路中斜壆，撼毀燈箱後，再全車翻轉四輪朝天，橫亘兩條行車線。女學神及姓馬師傅被困車內，消防員趕抵現場時，兩師徒已自行爬出車外，女學神手腳受輕傷由救護車送往醫院治療。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef9237a2b0fd82d1358e28809f8ce961ccb9b71c","tid":109783,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:03:58.000Z","msg":"呢啲臭閪根本唔應該揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 累人累物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e23fceb81ca5848e100d116097fe7a28415439","tid":109783,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86d1a90cad0708877f7e532c43d32cab2b73f88","tid":109783,"uid":15739,